{"tid":2173142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：會持謙卑的心服務香港 不會動用大量公帑 但有一系列加強治安的措施","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T10:09:45.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"1e24fd183a465da694b4479d31b20dea1aa042d2","tid":2173142,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥指，香港公共財政情況嚴峻，新一份施政報告不會動用大量公帑的新措施，但會有一系列加強香港在治安、經濟及公共衞生方面的防備措施。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光早前接受港台節目訪問，談到與林鄭月娥的關係時指，權力對人的負面影響很大，有時會令人忽略部分事情，林鄭月娥回應時指會持謙卑的心服務香港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥：「我沒有留意羅致光局長在談論我，我以為他在講談自己，由一名政客加入做官員，可能他自己有感受，對我以言，四十年如一日都是當時的初心，為了服務市民，我會以更謙卑的態度聆聽社會的意見。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=403035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403035&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=af980b22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D403035&h=de76abfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=403035</a>"},{"pid":"f0063a369bffad9bab89dcb2700e4b89388aaf7f","tid":2173142,"uid":127575,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"謙卑用心就唔會有反送中事件啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ba5316aa20fce1cba044238a3237e85a6921e7","tid":2173142,"uid":8308,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"治安? <br />\n除左警察打市民 <br />\n依一年都冇聽過有咩治安問題"},{"pid":"4e747c072a22c735e866c8139781c8ffe426f452","tid":2173142,"uid":202876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"理財新哲學唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61bbeb79364984bb7cee2263bb641be01dffc8